      "description": "In the laning phase, Use Ruby's 1st Skill to slow down the enemy, and the dash from her Passive to get closer. Then cast Ruby's Ultimate to pull the enemy into melee range and her 2nd Skill to keep them stunned. Finally, spam her Basic Attacks to finish them off."
